{"tid":1902772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【告急：TVB借疫情收視翻身】- 谷爆ViuTV、開電視收視計劃 (Fact checked)","createTime":"2020-02-28T14:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T09:57:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7138416f9e227d4f4858f8e2475ff0f2fd8871","tid":1902772,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"轉載<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/87458501_579379669585553_3590759016424275968_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=IEsVLiKD5m4AX9b-XBX&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=44480bce9be3044eeb8cde947a6f5a2f&amp;oe=5EB93A5C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F87458501_579379669585553_3590759016424275968_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DIEsVLiKD5m4AX9b-XBX%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D44480bce9be3044eeb8cde947a6f5a2f%26oe%3D5EB93A5C&h=34c98859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手share:</span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/posts/579380549585465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fposts%2F579380549585465&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=39468fe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/posts/579380549585465</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>隔離post問，點解ViuTV長期得3-5點</strong></span></span><br />\n喂你知唔知，你部電視<span style=\"color: red;\">冇「收視記錄儀</span>」，係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔計收視</span>ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算開著電視，點樣睇ViuTV、開電視都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點算好？</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抵制TVB戰線教你點做，方法由業內人士FC</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後有收視小知識<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">申請/ Login ViuTV acc</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(去網頁- <a href=\"https://viu.tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=7b919b01\" target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/</a> &gt; 右上角)<br />\n呢個Step好重要，<span style=\"color: red;\">方便ViuTV掌握觀眾數據</span>，用嚟sell廣告<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.S. 開電視仲未有會員制</span><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">用電腦或app，睇直播</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n⛔️<span style=\"color: red;\">好重要：對ViuTV, 開電視記得disable Adblock</span><br />\n👉🏻ViuTV - <a href=\"https://viu.tv/ch/99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fch%2F99&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=d2590c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/ch/99</a><br />\n👉🏻開電視 - <a href=\"http://www.hkopentv.com/#/live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkopentv.com%2F%23%2Flive&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=91e0742a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkopentv.com/#/live</a><br />\n👉🏻31台 - <a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=d8ea797e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv</a><br />\n(我哋建議大家真係要睇，否則品牌都可能認為數據有水份)<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">用電腦或app，重溫有興趣嘅節目</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個都好重要，<span style=\"color: red;\">方便電視台掌握數據，用嚟sell廣告</span><br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">進階：買FireTV 或Chromecast</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方便將電腦或app嘅畫面投射至電視機，享受睇電視樂趣 (下回分解，請留意日後嘅pinned post)<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【收視小知識】</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣計收視？<br />\n節目重溫一條數、電視機收視一條數、網上直播一條數、之後會加埋就係綜合收視 (即係跨平台收視)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2018 香港收視調查法<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/&hellip;/hk-tv-audience-measureme&hellip;/wireless-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fhk-tv-audience-measureme%E2%80%A6%2Fwireless-home%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=a178d25c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/&hellip;/hk-tv-audience-measureme&hellip;/wireless-home/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都市傳說，未經Fact check：<br />\n收視公司偏幫TVB係出哂名"},{"pid":"4c7fe6f2fa4e34d9e6f8470f86cc1a7b26a4c4bc","tid":1902772,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"Strong Post Leave My Big Name"},{"pid":"d1dc6259a9991cf72d30542395790f0fd1e95ff6","tid":1902772,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5029d838045487e73fc54dd98f40466900bb7f02","tid":1902772,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"公司機開兩個browser 24小時長睇冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bdd699ea91b6e9876f2999911630ab6b1d7d25","tid":1902772,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5029d838045487e73fc54dd98f40466900bb7f02","tid":1902772,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"公司機開兩個browser 24小時長睇冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT